I build systems that don't break at scale. With 10+ years architecting high-performance backends, I've delivered a 500x TPS increase at PayU (30→15,000/host) by rewriting critical paths in Rust, and slashed chat latency from 300ms to <75ms at Urban Company, boosting adoption from 32% to 47%.

Currently exploring AI/ML agents and backend automation as Co-Founder & CTO at [Hetu Labs](https://www.hetu-labs.com), where I'm applying lessons from payment systems, real-time platforms, and distributed architecture to the next generation of intelligent systems.
